<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>About Toornify</title>
    <%- include('partials/header.ejs') %>
  </head>
  <body
    style="
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #1e1b4b, #000000, #3b0764);
    "
  >
    <%- include('partials/navbar.ejs') %>

    <div class="min-h-screen mt-10 relative">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-8">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
            About Toornify
          </h1>
          <h2 class="text-xl text-white font-medium">
            India's Tournament Platform
          </h2>
        </div>

        <!-- Introduction -->
        <div class="mb-12">
          <p class="text-lg text-white leading-relaxed">
            Toornify is the ultimate destination{" "}
            <strong class="text-indigo-400">
              where gamers, creators, and organizers come together to compete,
              create, and grow. </strong
            >{" "} Our mission is to empower Indian talent and showcase it on
            the global esports stage, providing a professional, secure, and
            seamless platform for players and organizers alike.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Vision -->
        <section class="mb-12">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Our Vision</h3>
          <p class="text-lg text-white leading-relaxed">
            To position India as a global esports powerhouse, nurturing talent,
            tournaments, and creators, and connecting local gaming communities
            to international opportunities.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Mission -->
        <section class="mb-12">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Our Mission</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-indigo-400 mt-1">•</span>
              <span class="text-white"
                >Empower Gamers: Compete, improve, and gain recognition.</span
              >
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-indigo-400 mt-1">•</span>
              <span class="text-white"
                >Support Creators: Host tournaments and grow audiences.</span
              >
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-indigo-400 mt-1">•</span>
              <span class="text-white"
                >Enable Organizers: Professional tools for smooth, scalable
                event management.</span
              >
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-indigo-400 mt-1">•</span>
              <span class="text-white"
                >Celebrate National Pride: Highlight Indian talent while
                competing globally.</span
              >
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-indigo-400 mt-1">•</span>
              <span class="text-white"
                >Build a Thriving Community: Connect players, creators, and
                organizers in an inclusive and engaging ecosystem.</span
              >
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <!-- Why Toornify -->
        <section class="mb-12">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Why Toornify?</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-purple-400 mt-1">•</span>
              <span class="text-white"
                >Fair & Transparent: Advanced systems to ensure trustworthy
                competition.</span
              >
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-purple-400 mt-1">•</span>
              <span class="text-white"
                >Seamless Experience: Intuitive platform for registrations,
                match management, and leaderboard tracking.</span
              >
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-purple-400 mt-1">•</span>
              <span class="text-white"
                >Scalable & Secure: Reliable infrastructure for tournaments of
                all sizes.</span
              >
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-purple-400 mt-1">•</span>
              <span class="text-white"
                >Global Reach, Indian Pride: Promote Indian esports talent on an
                international stage.</span
              >
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <!-- Values -->
        <section class="mb-12">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Our Values</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-pink-400 mt-1">•</span>
              <span class="text-white"
                >Integrity: Transparent and fair competition.</span
              >
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-pink-400 mt-1">•</span>
              <span class="text-white"
                >Innovation: Cutting-edge technology for the ultimate esports
                experience.</span
              >
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-pink-400 mt-1">•</span>
              <span class="text-white"
                >Empowerment: Support every gamer, creator, and organizer.</span
              >
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-pink-400 mt-1">•</span>
              <span class="text-white"
                >National Pride, Global Outlook: Celebrate Indian talent while
                competing worldwide.</span
              >
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-pink-400 mt-1">•</span>
              <span class="text-white"
                >Excellence: Deliver world-class performance and security.</span
              >
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <!-- Motto -->
        <section class="mb-12">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Our Motto</h3>
          <blockquote
            class="text-xl font-semibold text-center text-white italic border-l-4 border-indigo-400 pl-6 py-4 bg-gray-800 rounded-r-lg"
          >
            "Every Game Counts. Every Player Matters. Proudly Indian, Globally
            Competitive."
          </blockquote>
        </section>

        <!-- Closing -->
        <div class="text-center">
          <p class="text-lg text-white leading-relaxed">
            Toornify is more than a platform it's a movement to elevate Indian
            esports, empower talent, and connect players, creators, and
            organizers globally. Every match and tournament strengthens India's
            presence in the esports world.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <%- include('partials/footer.ejs') %>
  </body>
</html>
